name: Visible Thoughts: 002
description:
002 of the Visible Thoughts series.

What's a life thrown in the black hole? Fear not the spit-back for the call attacks my soul either way and my breath chokes at the thought. I want eternity and a frozen capsule launching myself where I need to be, and where that is I've yet to know. But I hear and see and taste its air behind closed doors, the windows fettered and I cry and whine for more. How do I make my way back from the abyss with naught but the breath cut in my lungs?
